creator: TEMPLE Software
descriptionHtml:
EgoMenu is the global platform for online menus.

It is designed to create awesome, stylish, interactive menus for restaurants, pubs, cafes that want to get rid of old-style paper menus.

EgoMenu also helps hungry users find the best place for every occasion.

Restaurateurs use EgoMenu to:
• Create beautiful, dynamic online menus
• Add detailed dishes to the menus
• Update menus in real time
• Generate QR codes for the customers
• Gain exposure by showcasing their place to thousands of users
• Get new customers and increase revenue

Hungry eaters use EgoMenu to:
• Search for good restaurants, cafes, pubs, etc.
• Get information on the place (e.g. photos, opening hours)
• Browse up-to-date menus online
• Filter dishes according to needs (e.g. ingredients, allergens)
• View dish photos and details
descriptionShort: EgoMenu brings together a global community of good restaurants and hungry eaters

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
NEW Search bar:
You can now filter restaurants by location, cuisine, style, services and much more!

NEW dish numbers:
Each dish now has a unique number. Dish numbers are generated automatically or chosen manually by the restaurateur.
You can choose wether to show or hide dish numbers in each menu.

NEW Menu description:
You now have the possibility to provide a description for each menu. The description will be shown at the beginning of your menu.

Major UI improvements.

Minor bug fixes.
